parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose acceleration, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle shudders
misses gears
or fails to shift into the intended gear; the vehicle loses acceleration
even with the gas pedal floored; the transmission refuses to change gears; the vehicle slows down or stops moving without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the hybrid system can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The hybrid system fails to engage
causing the vehicle to stall or lose power; error messages appear on the infotainment system and dash; the vehicle makes a loud grinding noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the vehicle to accelerate can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle fails to accelerate when the gas pedal is pressed; the tachometer shows maxed-out RPMs
but the vehicle does not move; the vehicle slows down or stops moving without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The simultaneous failure of the brake and transmission systems can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle loses brake function and transmission function simultaneously; the vehicle coasts to safety without power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ICU module can cause power steering failure, instrument cluster failure, and other safety features to malfunction.
symptoms: Power steering is not as effective; instrument cluster fails; driver warnings like low tire pressure
blind spot detection
and others do not work; speedometer and miles driven stop working.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the forward collision avoidance system can cause the vehicle to suddenly apply the brakes at highway speeds, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The forward collision avoidance system activates without reason
applies the brakes at highway speed
and may occur multiple times during a single drive.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling and restarting issues can cause the vehicle to suddenly lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine dies and cannot restart
the vehicle stalls at red lights or stop signs
the dashboard lights come on
and the vehicle may take several minutes to restart.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The electrical system failures can cause various safety features to malfunction, leading to accidents or fires.
symptoms: The SRS light remains illuminated
multiple warning lights come on
the adaptive cruise control and start-stop systems malfunction
and the vehicle may experience a loss of power or acceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission and Idle Stop & Go System Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission and idle stop & go system issues can cause the vehicle to lose power, overheat, or even catch fire.
symptoms: The transmission electric oil pump may be damaged
leading to heat damage and potential vehicle fires
and the idle stop & go system may malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The brake system malfunction can cause the vehicle to lose braking ability, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The ABS and brake lights come on
the vehicle experiences a sudden loss of braking power
and the brakes may not respond to pedal input.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Oil Leaks and Oil Pan Gasket Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Oil leaks can cause the engine to seize, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded. Oil pan gasket failure can also lead to engine damage and costly repairs.
symptoms: Oil leaking from the engine
oil spots under the vehicle
oil dripping onto the ground
oil warning light illuminating
low oil levels
engine stalling or hesitation.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine misfires can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded. Injector failures can also lead to engine damage and costly repairs.
symptoms: Engine stalling
loss of power
engine misfire
check engine warning light illuminating
fuel odor detected while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Loss of power and acceleration can cause accidents or near-misses, especially when driving in heavy traffic or uphill.
symptoms: No power or acceleration
hesitation to accelerate
loss of motive power
engine stalling
check engine warning light illuminating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine shut-off while driving can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded, especially in heavy traffic or hazardous conditions.
symptoms: Engine shutting off while driving
icons on the dashboard turning red and flashing
"Engine Off" message displayed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Sudden acceleration and lurching can cause accidents or near-misses, especially when driving in heavy traffic or parking.
symptoms: Sudden acceleration or lurching
Rear Cross-Traffic Collision-Avoidance Assist system not engaging
rear distance warning system beeping.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The trim flying off while driving can cause distractions, accidents, or injuries to occupants or other road users.
symptoms: Trim pieces detach from the vehicle while driving
potentially causing damage to the vehicle or other objects.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden shattering of the sunroof can cause injuries, distractions, or accidents, especially if it occurs while driving at high speeds.
symptoms: The sunroof shatters without any apparent cause
raining glass into the vehicle's interior.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden loss of acceleration can cause accidents, especially if it occurs on a busy highway, and can lead to fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly stops accelerating
coming to a halt without warning
and may only be resolved by shutting off and restarting the engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The trunk door opening by itself can cause distractions, accidents, or injuries, especially if it occurs while driving.
symptoms: The trunk door opens unexpectedly
even when the vehicle is parked.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Stalling and Ignition Coil Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine stalling can cause accidents, especially if it occurs while driving, and can lead to fatalities.
symptoms: The engine suddenly stalls
and may not restart
accompanied by smoke from the tailpipe and an illuminated engine light.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A malfunctioning air conditioning system can cause discomfort, heat stress, or even lead to heat-related illnesses, especially in hot environments.
symptoms: The air conditioning system fails to cool the vehicle properly
even after extended periods of operation
and may not blow cold air.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine misfires can cause accidents, especially if they occur while driving, and can lead to fatalities.
symptoms: The engine misfires
accompanied by overheating
bad odors
and smog from the exhaust
and may be caused by contaminated fuel.
